'''Run''' ({{lang-en|''Truth''}}; {{lang-ar|حقيقة}}) waa sida ugu saxsan ee [[war]] ama xaalad tahay.<ref>[http://m-w.com/dictionary/truth  Merriam-Webster-def Merriam-Webster's Online Dictionary (truth)], [[2005]]</ref> Runta waxaa ka soo horjeeda [[been]]. Sidoo kale runtu waa sheegida xaqiiqada sida ugu saxsan ee dhacdo, war, marxalad iyo wixii la mid ah. Sida caadiga ah, inta ugu badan [[diin|diimaha]], filosofiga, iyo [[cilmi]]gu wuxu aad u dhiirigeliyaan sheegida runta, iyo in qofku noqdo mid run sheeg ah oo sida xaqiiqada ah wax u sheega.

[[Islaam|Diinta Islaamku]] waxay faraysaa dhamaan dadka muslimiinta ah ineey ahaadaan kuwo runsheeg ah, hadii kale waxay galayaan dembi lagu [[cadaab|ciqaabi]] doono aakhirada.

Guud ahaan, runtu waa soo gudbinta iyo ka waranka dhacdooyinka iyo macluumaadka xaqiiqada ah ee [[aduun]]ka ka dhaca maalin kasta taasi oo lagu soo gudbiyo si [[maqal]], [[muuqaal]] ama [[qoraal]] ah.<ref>Oxford English Dictionary (online): Definition of "narrative"</ref>

Addoommada Ilaahay runta way jecel yihiin.<ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/tacliinta-kitaabka/suʼaalo/ Suʼaalaha Kitaabka oo Laga Jawaabay]</ref>

